BEGIN_PGML Write an inequality to model the scenario. There is no need to solve the inequality.
A flatbed truck that hauls water is able to carry a maximum of [`[$end]\text{.}`] Water weighs [`[$speed]\text{,}`] and the plastic tank on the truck that holds the water weighs [`[$start]\text{.}`] How many gallons of water can the truck haul? Set up an inequality to answer this question. There is no need to solve it.
